h der Übersetzungen des Benjaminschen Werkes wird extensiv dokumentiert.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 4aBenjamin, Walter. 4aRezeption. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / German.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Literary and Cultural Studies - <1990z9783110637816oZDB-23-GLC0 cprintz978348435022940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311096202440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110962024423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110962024/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GLCb1990